file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https://localhost:8081/server/services/rest'
info:
  title: Devon Example
  description: Example of a API definition
  version: 1.0.0
  x-global: itIsGlobal
paths:
  /tablemanagement/v1/sampledata/:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Any
  /salesmanagement/v1/sampledata/:
    post:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Any
components:
    schemas:
        Table:
          x-component: tablemanagement
          x-test: testingAttributeTable
          x-global: iChangeGlobalVariable
          type: object
          properties:
            example:
              type: string
        Sales:
          x-component: salesmanagement
          x-test: testingAttributeSales
          type: object
          properties:
            example:
              type: string
